snippet.title: ASTRONAUTILUS trailer
snippet.description:
Link to the itch.io page: https://neozoid-games.itch.io/astronautilus-demo

I've been developing this game on my own since March of 2020, and I'm finally ready to release a demo to the public! I'm looking to release this game in summer of this year (likely July or August) - let me know if you all have any feedback! :D
